 -- Jordi Mallach <jordi@debian.org>  Sun, 21 Jan 2001 20:08:51 +0100

micq (0.4.6-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added patch from David Murn <davey@doa.org>:
    + changes behaviour of log writing. If STATUS_LOG is defined, only
      messages are written to the <uin>.log, so it's easy to see if someone
      said something while away (closes: #74559).
    + as a bonus, fix a potentially uninitialized variable in util_ui.c.
    Thanks David!
  * debian/rules:
    + start using DH_COMPAT=2.
    + replaced `pwd`s with $(CURDIR)s.
    + added support for DEB_BUILD_OPTIONS "debug". This also corrects CFLAGS
      a bit.
  * debian/control:
    + made debhelper's Build-Depend versioned for v2.
    + removed Suggests: menu.
    + updated Standards-Version to 3.2.1.0.

 -- Jordi Mallach <jordi@debian.org>  Sat, 16 Dec 2000 16:16:32 +0100

